      public String getCanonicalUrl()
      Description copied from interface: WithSystem
      Get the canonical URL(1) of the system.

      Note(1): while the method is called WithSystem.getCanonicalUrl() resources/elements/values can be sometimes annotated with a system url which is not a URL at all. In fact, in most cases it should not be necessary to treat this value as a URL
